<item>
            <title>[LU-12191] lctl list_param -R does not display everything</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-12191</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;While testing lnet sysfs patches, it is found that&#160; &lt;tt&gt;lctl list_param -R&lt;/tt&gt; does not display everything under sysfs tree.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The lnet-sysfs hierarchy is something like -&#160;&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;tt&gt;/sys/fs/lnet/net/o2ib1/ib0&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But &lt;tt&gt;lctl list_param -R&lt;/tt&gt; does not display anything beyond&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;tt&gt;/sys/fs/lnet/net&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is because of the below code in param_display function in&#160; -&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
tmp = strstr(paths.gl_pathv[i], param_name);
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here instead of &lt;tt&gt;param_name&lt;/tt&gt;, it should be /param_name/&lt;/p&gt;</description>
